ZMK_BASE_LAYER(LeftLinux,
    &kp LC(Q)   &kp LC(W)   &kp LC(E) &kp LC(R)  &kp LC(T)   ,  ___   &kp C_VOL_UP &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp LGUI  &kp C_PP         ,
    &kp LC(A)   &kp LC(S)   XXX       &kp LC(F)  &kp LC(G)   ,  ___   &kp LCTRL    &kp LALT      XXX       &kp RSHIFT,
